<li id="cite_note-suellentrop2005-2"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-suellentrop2005_2-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite id="CITEREFSuellentrop2005" class="citation magazine cs1">Suellentrop, Chris (November 7, 2005). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.slate.com/articles/arts/culturebox/2005/11/calvin_and_hobbes.html">"Calvin and Hobbes: The last great newspaper comic strip"</a>. <i><a href="/wiki/Slate_(magazine)" title="Slate (magazine)">Slate</a></i>. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20151103141705/http://www.slate.com/articles/arts/culturebox/2005/11/calvin_and_hobbes.html">Archived</a> from the original on November 3, 2015<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">December 16,</span> 2015</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Slate&amp;rft.atitle=Calvin+and+Hobbes%3A+The+last+great+newspaper+comic+strip&amp;rft.date=2005-11-07&amp;rft.aulast=Suellentrop&amp;rft.aufirst=Chris&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.slate.com%2Farticles%2Farts%2Fculturebox%2F2005%2F11%2Fcalvin_and_hobbes.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ACalvin+and+Hobbes" class="Z3988"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r951705291"/></span>
